Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:54.90,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな未来も　ふたりで見たかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:02:01.43,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}どんな想いも　伝わる距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:08.14,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}君の旅立ち　覚悟してたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:14.32,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}背中押す言葉　声にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:21.07,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}最後につよく　抱きしめたあと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:26.63,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}ぬくもりと同じだけの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:34.54,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀しみが　僕の心つつんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:40.67,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}優しくなるための　サヨナラ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:47.37,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}僕だけの幸せをくれたひと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.96,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}いつかまた会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:55.73,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}本当の君が見つかるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:03:01.45,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑顔忘れないで

Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:54.90,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}無論何種未來 都想一同見證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:02:01.43,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}有你伴我身畔 思緒才能傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:08.14,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}早已有所準備 你會踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:14.32,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,750)\blur2}幾欲衝口而出 終究未能表達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:21.07,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,750)\blur2}直至分別之際 深深擁抱過後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:26.63,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,300)\blur2}與溫暖同等份量的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:34.54,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哀傷將我的心包覆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:40.67,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\blur2}為了變得溫柔 就此別過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:47.37,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}令我獨佔幸福的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.96,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至再會之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:55.73,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}直至覓得真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:03:01.45,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}莫要忘記笑顏

Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞希子的送別會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就放在明天關門後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您了 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但亞希子也挺有兩下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然嫁了大自己15歲的老外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 店長有情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒啦 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒什麼八卦可聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一丁點也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼年紀輕輕就脫離戰線了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}完全不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}我也是突然來電的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打了幾個月的工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現現實果然嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比當路人甲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要痛苦百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情 明明心裡明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明心裡明白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}能在旅遊途中被搭訕 絕對是緣分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發什麼呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天上午有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想請你幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能請你十點左右來店裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到樓下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是幫我給亞希子挑禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能請你繞到後門來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來開門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有點緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先佈置明天的裝飾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來幫個忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞清缺什麼再去買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼容易就讓我進門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也意識一下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用費心…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無聲的宣戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡六花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒對她本人說過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑什麼告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是有男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甜茶可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯茶之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}俄羅斯茶：紅茶加果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花 臉上有果醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長 雖然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道你的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太殘酷了 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不買東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分頭買就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連句說明都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全不把我放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有急事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者說這做法太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我沒資格這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但居然沒開始就結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是身體不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有剩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有什麼留戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼果醬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真要回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶一道菜來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我負責帶喝的來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,複雜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 祝賀我們的亞希子結婚退職
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下個月就要在意大利生活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的想必不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊要作家庭主婦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他也勸我去上學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說店長和葉月君兩人會不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招到新人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐會時常來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真想現在就不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選打工時真不該帶著雜念的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那情況就算對方不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是相當失禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡那種豆芽菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦 亞希子醉了會哭的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更想哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去抽一根
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招牌背面居然是陽台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你抽煙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會得肺癌的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？ 三年以前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是可以吃的花蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和蔬菜差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長經常吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前整天買來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為丈夫喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然能看到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼胡話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說你能看到我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在搞怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有你這種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不喜歡電波男
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是六花的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說什麼沒有八卦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是有人生的伴侶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是生前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說直到死亡將我們分開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們結婚的誓言已經無效了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫島尾篤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾篤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾先生是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次被人意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的好像自己不存在一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是就在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你能看見我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長就是寡婦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她啊… 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以問一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個什麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個經常忘事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛手毛腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始開店的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訂單錯的像山一樣多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到病情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就急急忙忙的結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病情？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「笨蛋到死也治不好」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他的口頭禪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你一本正經的這樣說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說昨天為什麼頂條內褲就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想萬一被看到了能嚇退對方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是退避三舍了沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓六花幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是真死了就不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實很嚴峻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡六花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說你一點也不害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能會附身殺了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身體？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼真實感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是看得見摸不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你很危險耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好歹有點危機感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近我感覺自己不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先忠告你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從剛才不就說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒抽完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙頭處理好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡單說來 就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前流行的3D照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦聚焦看出立體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上想不起怎麼能看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能看出來的竅門 變成了習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算自己不想看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來要去送兩家貨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便吃個午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩小時左右回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事打手機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店裡就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到我想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟來店裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去二樓老實呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直飄著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一被人意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上又被討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確實夠煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從早到晚打量自己的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會膩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被她本人知道了絕對躲得遠遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不懷好意的盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒那個賊膽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管 我天生眼神凶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膽小也是天生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你這種莫名其妙的傢伙挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在沒興趣還嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電車遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是道口出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找店長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在去送貨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是打工的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是週六來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名叫島尾美穗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.89,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,島尾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是店長的大姑姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我老姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包隨手一放就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 島尾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會和店長重名的 請叫我美穗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那美穗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說週六來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是週四啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為明天是生日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六花的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 說到哪裡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想讓她休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就早來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之想讓她在生日這天放個好假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴的傢伙突然不做聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺似乎意味深長 讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然見面沒一會兒不該這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我討厭剪的花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去整天用過就扔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「那是給弟弟掃墓用的嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我始終問不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然 有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒看天氣預報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上新聞明明說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下就下起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但多虧美穗姐來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多賣兩盆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生日嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給開花店的送花不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下著雨呢 一起吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不是說在外面吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為下得突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送完貨就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我看店 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就30分鐘 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被隔著老公直呼名字了 有優越感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如拉麵…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶 葉月君 你有傘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長 你明天過生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美穗姐說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都這把年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼好祝賀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但每年還是會慶祝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是唯一的紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀念日？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這種事記不太住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在生日那天登了記
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是丈夫的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這事沒告訴那人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總是不遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說他不夠執著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「我死了就離婚」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「遺物都拿去扔掉」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點不講道理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿嘴都是「找別人去 找別人」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.90,0:18:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不管人家怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種說法反而是犯規的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不夠執著？ 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常誰能這樣決絕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決絕的活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是你這傢伙「死纏爛打」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿嘴漂亮話 把店長的心綁的緊緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫的心願也很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出個軌什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店長 不要轉移話題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是關鍵時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直 好喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是其實滿是老繭的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是圓圓的額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子更餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故人就像個故人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要獨霸著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我繼承吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麵會漲掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃熱的就會流出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是流鼻涕？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然… 能是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出彩虹了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們合打一把傘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙哪裡不夠執著了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打什麼傘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 島尾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早晚有一天 把你老婆睡走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎什麼

Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:31.89,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}いつも夢のなかでは　あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:39.15,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}どうして　ねえ　消えないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:43.24,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}I gave you everything. You gave me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.87,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}きっと　いつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:49.79,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}You're everything, still my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.04,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}愛しているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:22:05.43,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}真夏に降った雪のような　それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:15.77,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会わなければ　こんなに切なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:23.40,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}胸を締め付けることもなかった　それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:35.79,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}あなたに出会えなければ　強さも優しさも　知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:45.01,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}目を閉じれば　すぐそこに　あなたがいる

Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:31.89,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,750)}在夢中 你總帶著笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:39.15,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}為什麼 揮之不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:43.24,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我給了你全部 你給了我何物？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:46.87,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(750,500)}我堅信 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:49.79,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}你是我的全部 仍是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:53.04,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}我都深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:22:05.43,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}彷如夏日飛雪 那是如夢似幻的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:15.77,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}若沒有邂逅你 便不會如此五味雜陳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:23.40,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}不會心如刀絞 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:35.79,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}若沒有邂逅你 便不知何謂堅強與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:45.01,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(500,500)}合上眼簾 近在咫尺 有你相伴

